        PURPOSE OF TOOL IS TO ALLOW PEOPLE TO VISUALIZE OPEN KEYS

COLORSCHEME:
    Red for default keymaps that you never use.
    Orange for default keymaps that you may want to rebind.
    Green for selfmade.
    Yellow for pluginmade.
   
    

Have box on top of the keyboard showing current keystrokes that are entered in.
    If press delete, take out everything in keystrokebox and reset.
    If press leader, animate button press and then take to new keyboard.
    

Have box under keystroke box to describe what the last keypress did. IE if pressed i would give like some descrip like insert.
